name: WE NEED LIGHT
description:
WE ARE THE REFLEX THAT WE SEE ON WHAT WE GENERATE,
WHAT WE DO IS WHAT WE CARRY ON INSIDE,
WAHT WE ARE LOOKING AT IS THE PART OF US THAT WE SHARE.
LIKEWISE, LIKE ALWAYS, NATURE TEACH US:
EVERY REFLEX NEEDS LIGHT TO EXIST.

MY TRIP WAS ALWAYS DIRECTED TO RECOGNIZING WHAT I HAVE INSIDE OF ME.
